From: Stefan Berger <stefanb@linux.ibm.com>
Date: Fri, 3 Dec 2021 10:19:15 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 40/89] ima: Also allow MEASURE policy rules in the IMA
 namespace

Also allow MEASURE policy rules in the IMA namespace now.

Signed-off-by: Stefan Berger <stefanb@linux.ibm.com>
---
 security/integrity/ima/ima_policy.c | 3 +--
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 2 deletions(-)

diff --git a/security/integrity/ima/ima_policy.c b/security/integrity/ima/ima_policy.c
index e77809f560ac..7d84d5fe296b 100644
--- a/security/integrity/ima/ima_policy.c
+++ b/security/integrity/ima/ima_policy.c
@@ -1948,10 +1948,9 @@ static int ima_parse_rule(struct user_namespace *user_ns,
 			break;
 		}
 
-		/* IMA namespace only accepts AUDIT rules */
+		/* IMA namespace only accepts AUDIT & MEASURE rules */
 		if (ns != &init_ima_ns && result == 0) {
 			switch (entry->action) {
-			case MEASURE:
 			case APPRAISE:
 			case HASH:
 				result = -EINVAL;
